*[[1766]] &amp;ndash; [[Tiberius Hemsterhuis]], Dutch philologist and critic (b. 1685)
*[[1767]] &amp;ndash; [[Franz Sparry]], Austrian composer (b. 1715)
*[[1782]] &amp;ndash; [[Taksin]], King of Thailand (b. 1734)
*[[1789]] &amp;ndash; [[Abdul Hamid I]], [[List of sultans of the Ottoman Empire|Ottoman sultan]] (b. 1725)
*[[1789]] &amp;ndash; [[Petrus Camper]], Dutch anatomist (b. 1722)
*[[1801]] &amp;ndash; [[Noël François de Wailly]], French lexicographer (b. 1724)
*[[1804]] &amp;ndash; [[Toussaint Louverture]], Haitian Revolutionary (b. 1743)
