*[[1823]] &amp;ndash; [[Jacques Charles]], French chemist (b. 1746)
*[[1833]] &amp;ndash; [[Antoni Radziwiłł]], Polish politician (b. 1775)
*[[1836]] &amp;ndash; [[William Godwin]], English political writer (b. 1756)
*[[1850]] &amp;ndash; [[William Lisle Bowles]], English poet and critic (b. 1762)
*[[1858]] &amp;ndash; [[Anton Diabelli]], Austrian music publisher, editor, and composer (b. 1781)
*[[1868]] &amp;ndash; [[Thomas D'Arcy McGee]], Irish Nationalist, journalist, and Father of [[Canadian confederation]] (b. 1825)
*[[1871]] &amp;ndash; [[Alexander Loyd]], American politician, [[Mayor of Chicago]] (b. 1805)
*  1871   &amp;ndash; [[Prince Alexander John of Wales]] (b. 1871)
*[[1885]] &amp;ndash; [[Karl Theodor Ernst von Siebold]], German physiologist (b. 1804)
*[[1891]] &amp;ndash; [[P. T. Barnum]], American showman, businessman, scam artist, and entertainer (b. 1810)
*[[1920]] &amp;ndash; [[Karl Binding]], German jurist (b. 1841)
*[[1928]] &amp;ndash; [[Alexander Bogdanov]], Russian physician and philosopher (b. 1873)
*[[1932]] &amp;ndash; [[Grigore Constantinescu]], Romanian priest and journalist (b. 1875)
