*[[1943]] &amp;ndash; [[Jovan Dučić]], Serbian poet (b. 1871)
*  1943   &amp;ndash; [[Alexandre Millerand]], French politician, [[President of France]] (b. 1859)
*[[1947]] &amp;ndash; [[Henry Ford]], American automobile manufacturer and industrialist, founder of the [[Ford Motor Company]] (b. 1863)
*[[1949]] &amp;ndash; [[John Gourlay]], Canadian football player (b. 1872)
