*[[1955]] &amp;ndash; [[Theda Bara]], American actress (b. 1885)
*[[1960]] &amp;ndash; [[Henri Guisan]], Swiss army officer, General of the Swiss Army during [[World War II]] (b. 1874)
*[[1965]] &amp;ndash; [[Roger Leger]], Canadian hockey player (b. 1919)
*[[1968]] &amp;ndash; [[Jim Clark]], Scottish race car driver (b. 1936)
*[[1972]] &amp;ndash; [[Joe Gallo]], American gangster (b. 1929)
*  1972   &amp;ndash; [[Abeid Karume]], African political leader, first president of [[Zanzibar]] (b. 1905)
*[[1981]] &amp;ndash; [[Kit Lambert]], British record producer and manager (b. 1935)
*  1981   &amp;ndash; [[Norman Taurog]], American director (b. 1899)
*[[1982]] &amp;ndash; [[Brenda Benet]], American actress (b. 1945)
*  1982   &amp;ndash; [[Harald Ertl]], Austrian race car driver (b. 1948)
*[[1984]] &amp;ndash; [[Frank Church]], American Senator (b. 1924)
*[[1985]] &amp;ndash; [[Carl Schmitt]], German philosopher and theorist (b. 1888)
